      "qwen_observation": "The spring_boot_2_to_2_7 step failed compilation because upgrading to Spring Boot 2.7 pulled in Reactor 3.4, which moved the Retry class from reactor.retry to reactor.util.retry, causing type incompatibility errors.",
      "qwen_rationale": "Skipping the intermediate Spring Boot 2.7 upgrade avoids the Reactor 3.4 namespace breakage. Instead, jumping directly to Spring Boot 3.3 at JDK 17 leverages the UpgradeSpringBoot_3_3 meta-recipe, which is transitive and handles the full 2.x\u21923.x transition (including javax\u2192jakarta and Reactor migrations). Since UpgradeSpringBoot_3_3 internally composes the Java 17 build upgrade, the explicit upgrade_build_to_java17 step is removed."
